=Description= 

"a publication featuring essays curated and commissioned by Voluntary Arts to explore the potential of cultural commoning. This collection aims to demonstrate both the ways in which cultural commoning is already an inherent part of our local communities and their culture and also ways in which we might further develop this model as the basis for a future cultural ecology."

